Larsen P(1)(2), Elsoe R(3)(4), Graven-Nielsen T(5), Laessoe U(5)(6), Rasmussen 
S(3)(7)(4)(8).

Author information:
(1)Department of Occupational Therapy and Physiotherapy, Aalborg University 
